Title: Twisting kappa-deformed phase space
Authors: Piotr Czerhoniak (Institute of Physics, Zielona Gora Univ.)
Comments: LaTeX, 24 pages, 2 references added
\\
  We discuss the twisting procedure applied to the kappa-deformed space-time.
Two kinds of twisttings are considered, for both we introduce related phase
spaces. The changes of duality relations under the action of twist are shown.
